    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-06-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-06-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="975"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d975">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Chief Justice</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-06-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 13, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: At the request of Señor Don Joaquín Bernardo
                    Calvo, envoy extraordinary and minister plenipotentiary of Costa Rica, and of
                    Dr. Belisario Porras, envoy extraordinary and minister plenipotentiary of
                    Panama, I have the honor to transmit to you herewith a joint note<note n="1"
                        xml:id="d975fn1">The one next above.</note> addressed to you in which they
                    request you to accept the office of arbitrator of the boundary dispute between
                    their respective countries.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">P. C. Knox.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
